  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to tag other users in busy group or public chats so that they'll be more likely to see my message.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Tagging a user will notify them so they can find the mention in a group/public chat.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUser A types an \"@\" sign followed by User B's display name to tag them in a group or public chat.\r\n\r\nUser B receives a push notification which opens to User A's message within the chat.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/40890487-1cc7caba-6777-11e8-825c-61c97075ae9b.png\" width = 400/>\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nMentions aren't possible and users can easily miss responses from others.",
